text: Be in love with your life. Every minute of it.
Don't tell me the sky is the limit when there are footsteps on the moon.

Sometimes you will never know the value of a moment until it becomes a memory.
-Dr. Seuss
There's something in you that the world needs.

Accept who you are and revel in it.
-Mitch Albom

Allow yourself to hope, to believe and to trust again don't let a few bad memories stop you from having a good life!
-Mandy Hale
Focus on what matters and let go of what doesn't.
Set a goal that makes you want to jump out of bed in the morning.
Accept what is, let go of what was, and have faith in what will be.
Keep the faith. The most amazing things in life tend to happen right at the moment you're about to give up hope.
I'll never be perfect, but I can be better.
Don't worry about those who talk behind your back, they're behind you for a reason.

Spread love everywhere you go let no one ever come to you without leaving happier.
-Mother Teresa

Keep calm and carry on.
-Winston Churchill

Remember, today is the tomorrow you worried about yesterday.
-Dale Carnegie
I want to inspire people. I want someone to look at me and say, "because of you I didn't give up."
Don't wait for opportunity. Create it.

A person who never made a mistake never tried anything new.
-Albert Einstein

Start where you are. Use what you have. Do what you can.
-Arthur Ashe
The person who doesn't make mistakes is unlikely to make anything.
You will never have this day again so make it count.
Before Alice got to Wonderland she had to fall pretty hard down a deep hole.

A diamond is a chunk of coal that did well under pressure.
-Henry Kissinger
Once you let go of negative people, positive ones appear.
There's a story behind every person. There's a reason why they're the way they are. Think about that before you judge someone.
Whatever you want to do, do it. There's only so many tomorrows.

Life gives you lots of chances to screw up which means you have just as many chances to get it right.
-Carrie Bradshaw
I am in charge of how I feel and today I am choosing happiness.

Happy girls are the prettiest.
-Audrey Hepburn
You are responsible for your own happiness.
Stay true to you and you and you will end up incredibly happy.

Once you replace negative thoughts with positive ones, you'll start having positive results.
-Willie Nelson
It doesn't matter what others are doing. It matters what you are doing.
Say yes to new adventures.

Nothing can dim the light that shines from within.
-Maya Angelou
Don't be afraid to fail. Be afraid not to try.
What screws us up most in life is the picture in our head of how it is supposed to be.
The first step to getting what you want is having the courage to get rid of what you don't.
I hope you feel beautiful today.
It's gonna get harder before it gets easier. But it will get better, you just gotta make it through the hard stuff first.

Tell me and I'll forget. Show me and I may remember. Involve me and I learn.
-Benjamin Franklin
Don't tell me the sky is the limit when there are footsteps on the moon.

To make a difference in someone's life you don't have to be brilliant, rich, beautiful, or perfect. You just have to care.
-Mandy Hale

You are never too old to set another goal or to dream a new dream.
-C.S. Lewis
If you're not making someone else's life better, you're living yours wrong.
Confidence is not 'they will like me.' Confidence is 'I'll be fine if they don't.'
